    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Discovery of a new species and host record of Holophryxus Richardson, 1905 (Isopoda: Dajidae) from the central Arctic: a model of enhanced descriptive standards for epicaridean isopods" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8011019> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8011019>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Holophryxus citriformis sp. nov. Holotype, adult female: A, anterior part of body, showing cephalic and thoracic regions with associated limbs, ventral view; left pereopods and incubatory plate 1 omitted to show position of incubatory plates 2–4 (A1 = antennule, A2 = antenna, CP 1–4 = coxal plates 1–4, CR = cephalic ridge, IP1–5 = incubatory plates 1–5, Md = mandible, P5 = pereopod 5, SP = sternal plate); B, posterior part of body, showing spinous margins of incubatory plates (IP5) and position of anal opening (indicated by arrow)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8011019/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

